Description: Professional Cross-Platform Laser Cutting Software
 LumaBurn provides a high-performance, reactive interface for 
 OMTech, Longer Ray 5, and other GRBL-based laser cutters.
 .
 This package includes the core application and necessary udev 
 rules for hardware access.
